# Spec And Docs

- Link work items to roadmap, spec, and implementation artifacts.
- Every feature/bug ticket must include repo-linked spec, design, and validation docs.
- Keep spec and design docs updated in-place during implementation changes.
- Add a bottom addendum entry whenever original intent is changed, with reason.
- Update engineering patterns and testing docs when conventions evolve.
- Record architecture-impacting decisions in ADRs.
- Keep docs concise, current, and tied to shipped behavior.
